    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Fortifications constructed with salient and re-entering angles for obtaining an oblique, as well as a direct fire, and to afford shelter from an enfilade fire of the enemy.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
